\frac{\partial}{\partial a_{2 j}}\left[\ln W - \alpha_{1} \sum_{i} a_{1 i} - \alpha_{2} \sum_{j} a_{2 j} - \beta\left(\sum_{i} a_{1 i} \varepsilon_{1 i} + \sum_{j} a_{2 j} \varepsilon_{2 j}\right)\right] &= 0 \tag{7}
\end{align*}
\]

式中，\(\alpha_{1}, \alpha_{2}, \beta\) 为三个拉格朗日不定乘子。由式（6）和式（7）可得：热力学平衡态的分布为：

\[
